Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:07.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無重力的暗閻　唯有摸索前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:10.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:19.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同莫比烏斯環一般　命運九轉輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:22.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0.1}Win, Lose Or Draw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:28.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實究竟何在{\fnMS Gothic}？ {\fsp0}Lies & Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:34.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光影回轉{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}陰陽相生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:39.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運之骰一經擲出　就已無法停止轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:42.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Dive into the Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:50.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅之風揚　我只欲逆風直上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.79,0:23:53.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你緊緊擁入懷抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.13,0:24:01.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之劍{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}斬斷這一昏暗的時代
